column4: NSLOCTEXT("[ADC3C3814A09DDE67A71688CA2C66428]", "963051F642B2CD47F1C5E9A649D81681", "I\'m Devimon, a dark angel. I hold the power of darkness.")
NSLOCTEXT("[ADC3C3814A09DDE67A71688CA2C66428]", "10F4CE5B4E28F01DA61726A669B55E82", "Myotismon, is in the mansion. Maybe he\'s alive.")
NSLOCTEXT("[ADC3C3814A09DDE67A71688CA2C66428]", "128514C642F1E8BF9329D18BF0CB72E1", "I don\'t know...all I know is that you\'re my enemy.")
NSLOCTEXT("[ADC3C3814A09DDE67A71688CA2C66428]", "90FADB5045228D2CBACE6D83E712773E", "He got away! I don\'t like that guy.")
